@NODE copyright "Copyright"

This program is freely distributable, but also © by Michael Bauer. It may be
copied as long as no more than a nominal fee is charged to cover time and
copying costs. Permission is granted for CDs made by Urban Dominik Mueller,
Meeting Pearls, Fred Fish, Danny Amor and SaarAG (Martin Schulze).

This program uses triton.library, which is Copyright © Stefan Zeiger.

If you like this program, I'd like to encourage you, to leave me a note. This
will motivate me to improve this little program ;c)

@ENDNODE
@NODE intro "Introduction"

I've started to write this program a little while ago, because I wanted to
try out Triton. On the other hand, I was bored by the original Prefs program.

@ENDNODE
@NODE usage "Usage"

There's not much to say. The usage is like the original program, except that
you need Stefan Zeiger's Triton library.

@ENDNODE
