@NODE install "Installation"

Sorry, I'm to lazy to write an Installerscript now.

    You'll need to install the 'triton.library', e.g by starting the script
    in the Triton directory.

    Perhaps you'd like to install the catalog file.

    Copy the font program e.g to Sys:Prefs/

@ENDNODE
@NODE tooltypes "Tooltypes"

    EDIT
    SAVE
    USE
    CREATEICONS=YES|NO
    PUBSCREEN=<Pubscreenname>

@ENDNODE
@NODE shellargs "Shell Arguments"

    FROM,EDIT/S,USE/S,SAVE/S,PUBSCREEN/K

@ENDNODE

